287
00:13:15,810 --> 00:13:17,030
Maaari tayong magbago kung hindi ito gagana.

288
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:19,250
Nakahanap din ako ng mga backup na supplier.

289
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,100
